original_title: ウマのり娘がイクッ！製作費0円で私物販売、店舗突撃、イベント開催etc… 自力で稼いだお金で、競馬で勝って、AVを作ろう!!キミが中出ししても腰振るのやめない!ハメまくり射精しまくりスペシャル
overview: Ichika Matsumoto celebrates its 3rd anniversary! Production cost 0 yen start! A plan to make AV only with the money earned from horse racing based on the military funds earned by selling personal items and store assault guerrilla events. The goal is to go see his beloved horse, King, who was active as a racehorse. (Icchan is actually a horse owner!) With a punishment game where you let go of your horse if you fail the challenge... Use the help event (1000 pistons = 1 yen) to swing your hips hard! Earn production costs by using your own pussy for your beloved horse!
title: With no production costs, she sells her personal belongings, hits stores, holds events, etc… With the money she earns on her own, she wins a horse race and makes an adult film! Ichika Matsumoto
